document_type: Routing and Record Sheet, Notices, Propaganda, Interview, Article
summary: This document contains information on Alpha 66 activities in Los Angeles as of September 1970, including notices of meetings, propaganda, a history of Alpha 66, a picture of Vicente Mendez, a tape of a meeting/interview with Los Angeles leader Miguel Talleda, and a press interview with Andreas Nazario Sargent, Alpha 66 Secretary General in the US. It also includes articles and propaganda related to Alpha 66 activities and their impact on Cuba.
title: Alpha 66 Doings in Los Angeles as of September 1970
origin_agency: Los Angeles Office, Domestic Contact Service
